{"type": "article", "id": 15863, "title": "便携式的自行车车铃", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-10T07:51:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004521sJZqDfU5elGtYowM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款便携式的自行车车铃，来自米兰设计师 Odo Fioravanti 和意大利仪器品牌 Palomar。车铃另外配有一根带磁性的绑带，拴在自行车把上，就可以将车铃直接吸上去。取下车铃能直接揣在兜里，换另一辆自行车装上。按动车铃时，可以发出高达 80 分贝的声音，还能实现三种铃声都会循环播放。有黑、红、白三种颜色可选，售价 20 英镑。<a href=\"http://www.palomarweb.com/product/nello/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143151cIQXaPJd2lkC4L9Z.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"650\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79462103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143152PQEzvfdJs3WcVTgI.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"http://cms.qdaily.com/uploads/image/201510/44e589b27e11.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"650\" title=\" \" alt=\" \">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143309fy6BPpFhwkCvsiOS.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"212\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.2591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143310mvMTeztZLDQ3nsJd.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"222\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.27139364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}